{% extends "_includes/layout.njk" %}
{% from "_includes/macros.njk" import example %}
{% set title = "Accordion" %}

{% block content %}

  {% call example("Default") %}
<div class="accordion">
  <details name="accordion-demo" open>
    <summary>
      Is it accessible?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. It adheres to the WAI-ARIA design pattern.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-demo">
    <summary>
      Is it styled?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. It comes with semantic classes â€” no utility soup.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-demo">
    <summary>
      Is it animated?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. The chevron rotates smoothly on open/close.</div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endcall %}

  {% call example("Multiple Open") %}
<div class="accordion">
  <details open>
    <summary>
      What is Cider UI?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>An Apple-aesthetic UI component library built as a Tailwind CSS plugin.</div>
  </details>
  <details open>
    <summary>
      How do I install it?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Install with <code class="rounded-md bg-secondary px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">npm install ciderui</code> and import it alongside Tailwind CSS.</div>
  </details>
  <details>
    <summary>
      Does it support dark mode?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. All components support both light and dark mode using the <code class="rounded-md bg-secondary px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">.dark</code> class on the html element.</div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endcall %}

  {% call example("Disabled") %}
<div class="accordion">
  <details name="accordion-disabled">
    <summary>
      Available Section
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>This section is interactive and can be expanded or collapsed.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-disabled" class="pointer-events-none opacity-50">
    <summary>
      Disabled Section
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>This section cannot be interacted with.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-disabled">
    <summary>
      Another Available Section
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>This section is also interactive.</div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endcall %}

  {% call example("With Border") %}
<div class="accordion rounded-xl border">
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      What payment methods do you accept?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, and Apple Pay.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      Can I cancel my subscription?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>Yes. You can cancel anytime from your account settings. No questions asked.</div>
  </details>
  <details name="accordion-border" class="border-b last:border-b-0 px-4">
    <summary>
      Do you offer refunds?
      <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all plans.</div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endcall %}

  {% call example("In Card") %}
<div class="card max-w-md">
  <div class="px-6 pt-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Everything you need to know about the product.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion px-2 pb-2">
    <details name="accordion-card" open>
      <summary>
        How does billing work?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Plans are billed monthly or annually. You'll be charged at the start of each billing cycle.</div>
    </details>
    <details name="accordion-card">
      <summary>
        Can I change my plan later?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade at any time. Changes take effect on your next billing cycle.</div>
    </details>
    <details name="accordion-card">
      <summary>
        Is there a free trial?
        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div>Yes, we offer a 14-day free trial on all paid plans. No credit card required.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
{% endcall %}

{% endblock %}
